## Limitations

This report is based on data and literature available up to October 2023. The rapidly evolving nature of technology and platform strategies means that new developments may not be covered. Additionally, the focus on historical examples may not fully capture emerging trends in platform leadership. Future research could benefit from more recent case studies and data on newer platform companies.